"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-31-Former-Chinese-paddler-excited-to-make-Olympic-debut-at-58-for-Chile-1vGeX4mKUpy-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Former Chinese table tennis player Zeng Zhiying will make her Olympic debut at 58 at the 2024 Paris Games on behalf of Chile.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8182342623900017, \"rank\": 0.2212915283990403, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7295212790028219, \"rank\": 0.3601164287211183, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with CGTN Sports Scene's Greg Laffradi, the inspirational veteran shared her excitement as well as how she managed to stay competitive at this age.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.395760475821393e-22, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Very exciting.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my first Olympics, so I feel very happy and excited,\\\" Zeng said.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the Olympic stage, I just wanted to show my real abilities.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes at the Olympics are all very excellent, so I accomplished my task by just showing what I have got.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no difference among ages in competitions.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will face whoever you are against, no matter the age.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not feel I am much older than them.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel we are the same as competitors.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are equal on either side of the table.\\\"\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zeng became a professional player when she was 16.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the competitions in the Chinese national team has always been nothing but fierce because of the country's deep pool of talents for table tennis.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999376541938904, \"rank\": 3.953427186580152e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, Zeng wasn't able to play at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having retired as a player when she was 20, Zeng was then invited to Chile as a table tennis coach.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7295212790028219, \"rank\": 0.3601164287211183, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having picked up her paddle again during the COVID-19 pandemic, she was selected into the Chilean national team at 57.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9997789653371053, \"rank\": 0.0001659885384391019, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}, {\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999884039, \"rank\": 8.886063437216767e-12, \"text\": \"Chilean national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I usually train from Monday to Friday and play competitive matches on Saturday,\\\" Zeng said.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I train for half the day.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to train from morning to evening, but my body does not allow it.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to stay fit without injuries, I train around three hours a day and play both amateur and professional matches.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Depending on my physical level, if I can get through the trials and be selected, I will definitely continue playing table tennis.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am not selected, I will still play amateur matches.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The reason why I take part in competitions is that I am happy to play them and put pressure on myself, so I will continue playing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": []}]}"